                              <seg type="rubrication">Three pairs of lines on the opening page of <ref type="item" target="#p1_i2"/>
                                 alternating with black lines; title or incipit of the subsections of <ref type="item" target="#p1_i2"/>; name of St Mary on <locus target="#9ra"/>; 
                                 elements of punctuation marks and of Ethiopic numerals; tables on <locus from="2r" to="7v"/> and<locus target="#18rv"/>; some Ethiopic numerals in
                                 the tables on <locus from="2r" to="7v"/>.</seg>
